### Phase 2: Tray Icon Implementation

#### 3.7 Create electron/tray.js (NEW)
**Purpose:** System tray icon with context menu

**Requirements:**
- Always-visible tray icon
- Context menu: Show/Hide, Sync, Settings, Quit
